message.body: Do not spend your post trip time worrying. Spend it doing. And being around people you love and love you. Especially do not worry about men. Also. I have a cd for you
Thanks, sof. I'll do what I can to make it happen. What made you think of that?
I was thinking back to last summer and how i was so worried.
Yea. I don't even know what I'm feeling but anxiety is a big part of it. Not great at fixing that
Just know that its all a process
